FMLDOL
Factorio Mod Limited Distribution Only Licence
This software is provided without warranty and the software author/license owner cannot be held liable for damages.

Commercial Use
No. 
You are not allowed to make money off this factorio-mod or any of the contents.
You are allowed to feature the factorio-mod in other media, such as Twitch or YouTube.

Restricted. 
You may make alterations for your own private personal use only.
You are not allowed to distribute any content from the factorio-mod, or anything altered or derived from this mod with the following exceptions:
 - You may post modified sections of this factorio-mod in the mod's discord for the purpose of providing bug fixes or enhancements.
 - You may colaborate using github.

Distribution
You cannot distribute any content of the mod separate from the complete mod package.
You can distribute the complete and unmodified factorio-mod package with the following conditions: 
The mod must be an official release and must not be modified. (Packaging the mod into a larger zip file does not count as modification. It can be used in mod set packs.)
You must provide links to the mod on the mod portal https://mods.factorio.com and to the mod's discord.

For more information please join the mod's discord and speak to the mods/admins.

